Package: aws.swat.demo
Title: SWAT+ Ensemble on AWS with staRburst, Validated Against Open NWM Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Scott", "Friedman", email = "help@starburst.ing", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Demonstration project (not a CRAN package). Runs a SWAT+ BMP scenario
    ensemble across AWS workers via staRburst and validates simulated streamflow
    against the NOAA National Water Model retrospective from the AWS Registry of
    Open Data, with a visual Shiny front-end. Maumee River / Western Lake Erie.
